From a74fcf45f41560c89c3f05628920a89f2658cf7e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Foodiz Agent <agent@arena.ai>
Date: Thu, 14 May 2026 08:34:18 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat(auth): finish login/signup/reset/onboarding flows
 for all roles
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Backend (migration 0009):
- Add public.handle_new_user trigger on auth.users to create the
  profiles row server-side (the RLS layer in 0007 has no
  profiles_insert policy by design — blueprint v1.1 §6).
- Bootstrap loyalty_accounts for client signups.
- Add public.generate_referral_code helper.

Front-end:
- AuthProvider: drop the (RLS-blocked) client-side profile insert,
  add recoveryMode flag driven by PASSWORD_RECOVERY events, add
  signUp/signUpPartner/signUpCourier/updatePassword.
- AuthHomePage: wire pro signup buttons to /auth/partner and
  /auth/courier; redirect to /auth/reset-password during recovery.
- New pages:
  * /auth/partner & /auth/courier (ProSignupPage)
  * /auth/reset-password (set new password from email link)
  * /partner/onboarding (insert partners + upload SIRET/identity/
    KBIS to partner-documents-private with the path enforced by
    storage_partner_document_path_is_valid)
  * /courier/onboarding (insert couriers with validation_status=pending)
- PartnerHomePage / CourierHomePage now gate on validation_status
  and route brand-new pros to their onboarding.
- ProtectedRoute respects recoveryMode and pins the user to the
  reset-password screen until they pick a new password.

Docs: AUTH_IMPLEMENTATION_NOTES.md
